column3: NSLOCTEXT("ContractTable", "74666AF948E75585AFB957A6FE2D76B8", "This is the first contract in Torchlight Frontiers. The system, like most of the game, is a work-in-progress. We hope you will jump in and earn some useful loot while giving us feedback and bug reports. More content, more types of loot, and exclusive cosmetics are in development for the full release of Contracts. \r\n\r\nThe upgrade to Premium tier is free for all alpha testers this season. Come on in and get that Fame!")
column5: NSLOCTEXT("ContractTable", "438CB46142DB93800F7127B1688BD7B9", "Imperial Agents in every outpost are offering the New Beginnings Contract! See Intelligence Agent Bray to get started. ")
